Installation:

to compile:
qmake && make

to install:
sudo make install

Uninstallation:

sudo rm -rf /usr/cydra                                                <-- All of yours settings
sudo rm -f /usr/bin/a2wm && sudo rm -f /usr/bin/start_a2wm.sh            <-- The WindowManager

/!\ STILL IN AN VERY EXPERIMENTAL VERSION /!\
